Product Version     25.10    Cadence Design Systems, Inc.
timing_report_...ly_late_header(25.10)  timing_report_...ly_late_header(25.10)

Name
       timing_report_unconstrained_path_early_late_header

Syntax
       timing_report_unconstrained_path_early_late_header

       {true | false}

       Default: false

       When  set  to true, the software provides information in the timing re-
       port header that indicates whether an unconstrained path is a  late  or
       early path.

       To set this global variable, use the set command.

